Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Derek Fisher?

Derek Fisher is 50 years old.

Where was Derek Fisher born?

Derek Fisher was born in Little Rock, Arkansas.

When was Derek Fisher born?

Derek Fisher was born on August 9, 1974.

How tall is Derek Fisher?

Derek Fisher is 6-1 (185 cm) tall.

How much did Derek Fisher weigh when playing?

Derek Fisher weighed 200 lbs (90 kg) when playing.

Is Derek Fisher in the Hall of Fame?

Derek Fisher is not in the Hall of Fame.

When was Derek Fisher drafted?

Derek Fisher was drafted by Los Angeles Lakers, 1st round (24th pick, 24th overall), 1996 NBA Draft.

What position did Derek Fisher play?

Point Guard and Shooting Guard.

When did Derek Fisher retire?

Derek Fisher last played in 2014.

What is Derek Fisher's net worth?

Derek Fisher made at least $63,238,057 playing professional basketball.

How much did Derek Fisher make?

Derek Fisher made $6,373,900 in 2008.

What did Derek Fisher average?

Derek Fisher averaged 8.3 points, 2.1 rebounds, and 3.0 assists per game.

How many rings does Derek Fisher have?

Derek Fisher won 5 championships.

What is Derek Fisher's Twitter account?

Derek Fisher is on Twitter at derekfisher.

What schools did Derek Fisher attend?

Derek Fisher attended Parkview in Little Rock, Arkansas and Little Rock.

What are Derek Fisher's nicknames?

D-Fish is a nickname for Derek Fisher.
